<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=10776&amp;p=122242#p122242"><![CDATA[
Sometimes the rat disappears in the rat race of Battletoads. If you make it to the bomb, you can't progress because the rat won't die, and there's no way for you to die so your game is stuck. This is a good reason for arcade games and other games to have kill timers, the ensured death gives a way for the game to recover.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=5165">rainwarrior</a> — Tue Dec 10, 2013 3:33 pm</p><hr />
